---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Assert the current page title

Usage: bl expect title [OPTIONS] <operator> <text>

Arguments:
  <operator>  Comparison: contains (substring) or equals (exact match) [possible values: contains, equals]
  <text>      Expected title or title substring

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl expect title contains "Dashboard"
  # Pass if the title contains Dashboard
